                            <comment id="13608941" author="bmargulies" created="Thu, 21 Mar 2013 13:55:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve revised the design of this a bit.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve factored out an AbstractLuceneIterator, with an abstract method &lt;br/&gt;
org.apache.mahout.utils.vectors.lucene.AbstractLuceneIterator#getVectorName, called at each iteration.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The plain LuceneIterator just arranges to fetch the id field, and return the value from this method.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Other subclasses can fetch more fields and provide accessors.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13609006" author="hudson" created="Thu, 21 Mar 2013 14:57:29 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Integrated in Mahout-Quality #1915 (See &lt;a href=&quot;https://builds.apache.org/job/Mahout-Quality/1915/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://builds.apache.org/job/Mahout-Quality/1915/&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;br/&gt;
